chart.name: Network Usage (bits/sec)
chart.programText:
A = data('net.usage.average', filter=filter('object_type', 'vm')).scale(8192).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).min().publish(label='B')
C = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='E')
F = (A).max().publish(label='F')

chart.name: Top VMs by Uptime (days)
chart.programText:
A = data('sys.uptime.latest', filter=filter('object_type', 'vm') and filter('metric_source', 'vsphere')).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A/(3600*24)).top(count=5).publish(label='B')
